        <p>The WSO2 Task Server is an convenient way to do shedule remotely triggered schedule tasks in the web!
        </p>

        <p>The WSO2 Task Server is built on top of the WSO2 Carbon platform. It utilizes
            many features made available by the Carbon platform. A task can be scheduled where
	    a simple HTTP URL can be given to be called according to the scheduling criteria.
        </p>

